  <name>WatchMate</name>
  <summary>InfiniTime companion app</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Sync your PineTime smart watch running InfiniTime firmware with your Linux desktop or mobile.
      Visually optimized for GNOME.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Serve current time to the watch</li>
      <li>Read various data form the watch</li>
      <li>Perform OTA firmware update from DFU files or GitHub releases</li>
      <li>Automatically check for available firmware updates</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Roadmap:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Media player control</li>
      <li>Notifications</li>
      <li>Secure pairing</li>
      <li>Application settings</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

